- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a generative model for networks with community structure and applies local approximation techniques.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely as the paper does not focus on data structures and algorithms specifically.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is even less likely as the paper does not focus on systems and control specifically.
